 EIS instrument is presented and an\ninstrumental effect, possibly related to a distorted point spread function,\nthat affects velocity measurements is identified.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Jul 2011 18:25:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-28"}
